data.headline: Unprotected
data.description: Covax, a WHO-backed program to get Covid-19 vaccines to the world's poorest countries, was left short of doses when its biggest supplier, the Serum Institute of India, stopped exporting.
data.title: Free vaccine doses allocated and delivered through Covax, select regions
